&nbsp;
"Once again this is the demonstration of the state in which the metropolitan city of Palermo pours, which is not able to guarantee the necessary safety and reliability not only to those coming out for a trivial walk but also to those who daily conduct and carry on their work - add Fazzese and Brugnone - A job, in the case of the Riders, penalized by all the degenerations that there are in the city, including the condition of the streets full of holes: those who work on motorcycles or bikes, more than in the evening, to make deliveries at home, is the first to make their expenses. This only the new case, we denounced many episodes of violence against riders, robbed, assaulted, beaten, mostly in the historic center. This new episode at the Cep raises the concern even more."
&nbsp;
"We ask that the Municipality of Palermo and the mayor do not remain deaf to our requests, as has happened so far, but they convoke us to address in the shortest possible time the numerous problems of riders - add Fazzese and Brugnone - In February we sent a request for meeting the Forzinetti and Carta councillors but never answered. And we are thinking of asking the various platforms that operate on the square of Palermo, Glovo, Deliverooo and Just Eat, the interdition of the delivery of orders over a certain time in certain areas of Palermo".

